summary: The first of the Uchiha has come to Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
The first of the Uchiha has come to Skyrim.
Hylla is a character that I recently made and was not originally going to be anything but a nord or one of my Brute/Amazon characters but I decided to change her a bit.

-Required Mods-

ApachiiHair
Crimson Tide - Blood
Naruto Eyes (search Naruto and pick the overhaul)
Blades of Sithis (search Sasuke for Uchiha retexture [it has the meshes and .esp file included])
Brute Amazon Pack (included in file)

-Notes-
Includes three saved files, one Brute, one amazon, and one nord save.
I\'m using CBBE face textures and body mod so to get her looking like that as well use CBBE. Not required.
author: cook104
